imageDescriptions.description: WIDE SHOT of the throne room with Alexander (8-12, medium brown tousled hair, green eyes, wearing a hoodie) and Adrian (7-9, curly ginger hair, bright sky-blue eyes, wearing a casual jacket) standing before a stern, greedy king. LIGHTING: warm golden hour beams through stained glass, creating long dramatic shadows across marble floors. FOREGROUND: the boastful miller, chest puffed, pointing toward the boys. MIDGROUND: Alexander and Adrian, nervous but determined, small figures against the throne. BACKGROUND: opulent throne, courtiers in dim silhouettes. MOOD: tense, anxious, a touch of mischief. Watercolor illustration style, Axel Scheffler inspired, with textured washes and expressive linework.

CLOSE-UP of Alexander (green eyes, tousled brown hair, hoodie) and Adrian (curly ginger hair, bright sky-blue eyes, casual jacket) in a dim turret room. LIGHTING: candlelit, warm flicker meets cool moonlight, creating soft dramatic shadows. FOREGROUND: a shimmering nebula-like web, delicate and translucent. MIDGROUND: the boys' hands carefully untangling threads, faces lit by candle glow and concentration. BACKGROUND: a tall shadow forming into the Nebelhexe, dark hair and warm yet mysterious expression. MOOD: tense wonder, eerie beauty. Watercolor illustration style, Axel Scheffler inspired, with delicate textures and luminous washes.

imageDescriptions.chapterTitle: Die zweite und dritte Nacht — Neonfäden und schleichende Versprechen
imageDescriptions.description: DRAMATIC ANGLE of a neo-royal workshop under neon lights. LIGHTING: cool neon blues and hot magentas create stark contrasts, reflective chrome surfaces gleam. FOREGROUND: Alexander (medium brown wavy hair, green eyes, hoodie) and Adrian (short curly ginger hair, sky-blue eyes, jacket) working on glowing data-threads, fingers moving fast. MIDGROUND: Nebelhexe with dark hair, warm yet mischievous smile, collecting trinkets. BACKGROUND: hovering drones, copper domes, a distant throne room window lit in gold. MOOD: tense escalation, techno-fairytale collision. Watercolor illustration style, Axel Scheffler inspired, with vivid neon washes and crisp ink outlines.

imageDescriptions.chapterTitle: Hochzeit, Verlust, und eine ungewöhnliche Idee
imageDescriptions.description: HERO SHOT of a royal nursery scene. LIGHTING: soft moonlight through rain-streaked windows, warm lamplight near the cradle. FOREGROUND: Alexander (green eyes, tousled hair, hoodie) gently holding the baby; Adrian (curly ginger hair, sky-blue eyes, jacket) reading from a small book. MIDGROUND: the Nebelhexe (dark hair, warm mysterious face) sitting oddly still, watching and learning. BACKGROUND: the ornate royal bed and rainy city lights. MOOD: fragile hope, uneasy bargain, human warmth confronting otherness. Watercolor illustration style, Axel Scheffler inspired, with gentle washes and expressive characters.

imageDescriptions.chapterTitle: Die Enthüllung — Regen aus Neon und ein Name, der alles verändert
imageDescriptions.description: WIDE SHOT of a rain-soaked cyber-forest near a rusted radio tower. LIGHTING: neon reflections on wet surfaces, dramatic wet sheen, soft moonlight over the tower. FOREGROUND: the Kurierjunge hiding behind a wall with a small recorder. MIDGROUND: Nebelhexe at the tower, dark hair lit by neon, adjusting fog-emitters and singing; her mouth forms a clear, revealing word. BACKGROUND: Alexander (hoodie) and Adrian (jacket) in the throne hall watching the playback on a tiny device, expressions of dawning triumph. MOOD: triumphant revelation, bittersweet victory, cyber-noir fairytale. Watercolor illustration style, Axel Scheffler inspired, with luminous neon washes and textured ink marks.
